OL,3,CTwo men charged after firearms and
OL,4,Cammunition discovered in car
OL,6,FPolice Scotland have charged two men
OL,7,Fafter they say a firearm and
OL,8,Fammunition were discovered in a car
OL,9,Fnear Lockerbie.
OL,11,FThe force said it was part of efforts
OL,12,Fto tackle serious and organised crime,
OL,13,Fand that officers acted on
OL,14,Fintelligence stopping the vehicle on
OL,15,Fthe M74 just before 8pm on Friday (29
OL,16,FMay).
OL,18,FTwo men, aged 35 and 39, were arrested
OL,19,Fand charged in connection and are due
OL,20,Fto appear before Dumfries Sheriff
OL,21,FCourt on Monday (1 June).
