OL,3,CTwo men charged after firearms and
OL,4,Cammunition discovered in car
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Steven
OL,7,FElliott said: "Firearms clearly cause
OL,8,Frisk and harm to our communities, and
OL,9,Fthis recovery sends a clear message to
OL,10,Fthose involved that we will not
OL,11,Ftolerate their illegal activities.
OL,13,F"We remain absolutely committed to
OL,14,Ftackling serious and organised crime
OL,15,Fand information from the public is
OL,16,Fvital to this work.
